column2: SELECT u.up_name as name, x.objID,     p.ra, p.dec,    dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,    p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, s.z as redshift, p.modelMag_z FROM #upload u       JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id       JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID       LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID ORDER by x.up_id
